graph TD
    UserCode[User Program: RDD / DataFrame Code] -->|Evaluated Lazily| Lineage[Logical Plan: RDD Lineage Graph]
    Lineage -->|Action Triggered| DAG[DAG: Directed Acyclic Graph of RDDs]
    
    subgraph "DAGScheduler (Logical Compilation)"
        DAG --> StageBuilder[Build Stages]
        StageBuilder -->|Narrow Transform| Pip[Pipeline Operations in Single Stage]
        StageBuilder -->|Wide Transform| ShuffleBound[Create Stage Boundary at Shuffle]
        Pip --> StageSet[List of Stages: Stage 0, Stage 1...]
        ShuffleBound --> StageSet
        StageSet --> TaskSetGen[Generate TaskSet for each stage]
    end
    
    subgraph "TaskScheduler (Physical Execution)"
        TaskSetGen --> Schedule[Locality-aware Task Scheduling]
        Schedule --> ClusterManager{Cluster Manager Resources?}
        ClusterManager -->|Available| ExecRun[Distribute Tasks to Executors]
        ClusterManager -->|Starved| Delay[Wait for free Slots / Delay Schedule]
    end
    
    subgraph "Worker Nodes"
        ExecRun --> Run[Run Task Threads in JVM Executor]
        Run -->|Task Success| Complete[Notify TaskScheduler]
        Run -->|Task Failure| Retry[TaskScheduler Retries Task max 4x]
        Retry -->|Max retries exceeded| Fail[Fail Stage / Job]
    end
